 entire life."],[4220,4371,"Okay?"],[4404,4600,"Well, then don’t do it again."],[4754,5005,"Just be honest with me for once."],[5005,5030,"Okay?"],[5030,5251,"I am so, so"],[5251,5513,"sick of you claiming to be protecting me"],[5513,5584,"and expecting me"],[5584,5730,"to just go along with everything."],[5730,5851,"Vincent?"],[5855,6006,"You don’t understand!"],[6389,6477,"If you knew the truth,"],[6477,6648,"then you would be terrified of me."],[7190,7273,"I don't care."],[7703,7945,"I need to know who the man I love is."],[8078,8195,"I need to know"],[8195,8379,"what kind of father Jimmy has."],[8971,9059,"What is going on?"],[9059,9175,"Aunty Fiona,"],[9175,9238,"what are mommy and"],[9238,9405,"Mr. Price fighting about?"],[9509,9605,"Something they should"],[9605,9768,"have talked about eight years ago."],[9768,9864,"Just give them some space,"],[9864,9976,"kiddo. Okay?"],[9980,10026,"Who knows?"],[10026,10130,"You might just have a new daddy"],[10130,10281,"for your birthday this year."],[10356,10393,"Quick!"],[10393,10447,"Out of the way!"]],"39":[[45,104,"Move aside!"],[104,262,"This patient is in critical condition."],[2052,2198,"Just give me some time, Ella."],[2335,2456,"Please."],[2510,2552,"Jimmy!"],[2552,2673,"Where are you going?"],[2915,3023,"Jimmy?"],[3182,3303,"Jimmy!"],[3403,3511,"Jimmy’s over there."],[3516,3641,"He just took off all of a sudden."],[3970,4045,"Jimmy?"],[4617,4733,"Let me in!"],[4779,4900,"Let me in!"],[5317,5438,"Jimmy!"],[5447,5534,"Oh!"],[5534,5659,"Ugh, these are new."],[5834,5918,"Jimmy,"],[5918,5976,"Jimmy,"],[5976,6026,"Jimmy,"],[6135,6197,"Hey, don’t scare me okay?"],[6197,6281,"Okay, don’t..."],[6285,6373,"Go!"],[6373,6473,"What are you doing?"],[6581,6652,"Help!"],[6656,6685,"Help!"],[6685,6765,"I need help over here!"],[6765,6886,"Somebody help!"],[7040,7248,"Why is he so attracted to blood?"],[7286,7415,"Is it just a coincidence?"],[7482,7590,"Or is..."],[7590,7707,"Jimmy, my son?"]],"40":[[496,575,"Ella, don't worry."],[613,692,"His test came back good."],[729,863,"He's gonna wake up any minute now."],[925,1046,"I know."],[1117,1313,"He's never passed out like this before."],[1313,1422,"But what if happens again?"],[1422,1518,"I'm not there to help."],[1518,1584,"What if..."],[1772,1893,"Before he collapsed,"],[1926,2064,"he was chasing that trail of blood"],[2064,2152,"down the hallway."],[2344,2519,"Ella..."],[2519,2598,"Mommy!"],[2798,2907,"Hey!"],[3182,3249,"Mommy?"],[3249,3311,"Yeah,"],[3311,3432,"you're awake."],[3495,3653,"Oh, you scared me."],[3766,3883,"What was that?"],[3883,4012,"Why were you running"],[4012,4149,"after that woman down the hallway?"],[4404,4525,"I don't remember."],[4800,4884,"Okay."],[5075,5196,"That's okay."],[5480,5597,"Mr. Price!"],[5789,5876,"Mommy,"],[5876,6047,"Auntie Fiona said that"],[6047,6285,"after you and Mr. Price finish fighting,"],[6285,6452,"Mr. Price would become my daddy."],[6656,6852,"So is he my daddy now?"],[6931,7019,"Oh."]],"41":[[87,316,"What nonsense"],[316,458,"Auntie Fiona has been feeding you."],[558,654,"Mr. Price."],[654,800,"I want a daddy for my birthday."],[846,946,"Can you marry mommy"],[946,1017,"before then?"],[1017,1163,"My birthday is—"],[1297,1422,"Why would she hide his birthday?"],[1530,1755,"Unless...she was already pregnant"],[1755,1876,"before we broke up."],[1939,2135,"Oh, no no no no no no, this is bad."],[2135,2189,"This is bad."],[2189,2373,"I'm not ready for the truth to get out."],[2414,2565,"Let Jimmy finish speaking Ella."],[2690,2840,"I'd love to hear what he has to say."],[3103,3257,"Well, that is rich"],[3257,3420,"coming from the king of lies."],[3611,3757,"If you can't be transparent"],[3757,3812,"with me."],[3858,4033,"Vincent, do not expect me"],[4033,4154,"to be that with you."],[4446,4504,"It's late."],[4504,4625,"You should probably go."],[4788,4959,"Mommy, I don't want Mr. Price"],[4959,5042,"to leave."],[5138,5259,"Hun..."],[5359,5559,"I want a daddy who read me stories"],[5559,5630,"before bed."],[5680,5801,"Everyone else has one."],[5822,6001,"So can Mr. Price please stay?"],[6790,6911,"Okay."],[7332,7494,"I think that's a yes."],[7578,7695,"Really, mommy?"],[7974,8128,"Yes. Really."],[8812,8975,"Being with Jimmy like this feels..."],[9067,9188,"right."],[9288,9409,"Tonight,"],[9413,9488,"I'm gonna find out"],[9488,9597,"if he's really my son."]],"42":[[1730,1910,"Ella, I am so close"],[1910,2039,"to uncovering your secret."],[2706,2823,"Boss."],[2844,3007,"We ran into a few of your father's men"],[3007,3103,"nearby."],[3123,3228,"But don't worry."],[3257,3378,"We made quick work of them."],[3445,3586,"Those fuckers just keep coming, huh?"],[3749,3870,"Watch over them for a bit."],[3945,4029,"I'll be right back."],[4029,4129,"Yes, sir."],[4383,4508,"Fiona, are you free right now?"],[4642,4779,"I need to talk to you about Jimmy."],[6877,6919,"Hey, kid."],[7057,7144,"Where do you think you're going"],[7144,7194,"at this hour?"]],"43":[[592,713,"Jimmy?"],[1505,1622,"Jake."],[1672,1793,"Jake. Hey!"],[2097,2193,"Oh my god."],[2235,2356,"Where are Jimmy and Vincent?"],[2882,3003,"Jimmy?"],[3053,3174,"Jimmy. Where are you?"],[3345,3536,"So you finally figured it out, huh?"],[3566,3687,"Took you long enough."],[3691,3812,"Idiot."],[3933,3991,"You really think"],[3991,4104,"after the way you treated me,"],[4104,4220,"I would have your child?"],[4425,4479,"No."],[4621,4742,"But yes,"],[4742,4863,"Jimmy is your son."],[5088,5271,"The one Ella wanted to keep"],[5309,5467,"even after you dumped her."],[5563,5843,"The one she almost died giving birth to."],[5960,6081,"Yeah."],[6114,6231,"You're that kid's father."]],"44":[[959,1080,"Jake."],[1092,1134,"Jake!"],[1134,1251,"Wake up!"],[1288,1409,"Shit."],[1547,1668,"Where'd they go?"],[1755,1810,"My father"],[1810,1914,"must have sent someone."],[1972,2093,"Ella, Jimmy."],[2131,2252,"Please be okay."],[3470,3591,"Jimmy, is that you?"],[3891,4008,"Jimmy!"],[4012,4133,"Put that down!"],[4200,4320,"Oh god. There's blood on it."],[4366,4450,"What are you doing?"],[4450,4529,"What?"],[4571,4692,"Mommy!"],[4696,4725,"What?"],[4725,4842,"Where are we?"],[4842,4992,"What? Hey! Hey!"],[5042,5163,"What is happening?"],[5213,5334,"What?"],[5455,5693,"Is that what you are after earlier?"],[5809,5947,"You want blood?"]],"45":[[41,162,"I didn't mean to."],[208,262,"I didn't."],[275,383,"I didn't mean..."],[429,579,"Jimmy likes blood."],[767,888,"Just like Vincent."],[2064,2177,"How could I've been so blind?"],[2177,2398,"Vincent and Jimmy are both vampires."],[2652,2765,"If I just would have"],[2765,2848,"figured it out sooner,"],[2848,2902,"I could have"],[2902,2994,"prepared Jimmy for this."],[3061,3182,"Please don't hate me, mommy."],[3207,3286,"I'm not a monster."],[3286,3353,"I promise"],[3353,3465,"I won't have blood anymore."],[3570,3691,"Don't leave me."],[3728,3853,"Oh my god! I would never."],[3853,3987,"I would never leave you. Okay?"],[3987,4116,"I don't hate you, I promise."],[4170,4266,"I'm so sorry."],[4266,4391,"This is not your fault."],[4391,4512,"This is my fault."],[4850,5013,"There's a little one too?"],[5034,5113,"I can't wait"],[5113,5288,"to tell the Count about his grandkid."]],"46":[[1255,1376,"You're here."],[1422,1543,"Uncle Vincent."],[1605,1735,"Are you a superhero?"],[1801,1943,"I'm glad you view me as a hero,"],[1943,1985,"Jimmy."],[1985,2081,"But..."],[2193,2318,"Please don't call me your uncle."],[2464,2544,"- Ella, I need to— - Vincent, I need to"],[2544,2640,"talk to you about something."],[3028,3057,"Look,"],[3057,3128,"about Jimmy."],[3128,3178,"No."],[3549,3670,"Let me go first."],[4045,4166,"I know your secret."],[4454,4633,"Mr..."],[4688,4800,"Vampire?"]],"47":[[54,179,"I don't know what you're talking about."],[283,479,"Stop lying to me, Vincent."],[1676,1730,"Ella?"],[2085,2189,"Ella, get down from there!"],[2189,2318,"You're crazy. You're gonna fall!"],[2373,2469,"I wonder what would happen"],[2469,2548,"if I did fall."],[2723,2756,"You know,"],[2756,2877,"I picked this place for a reason."],[2911,2973,"Vincent."],[3040,3107,"Do you recognize it?"],[3199,3336,"This is where we first reunited."],[3336,3541,"This is where you saved me."],[5209,5367,"I did not dream that white-haired man."],[5367,5488,"He was real."],[5722,5843,"He was you."],[6051,6172,"Are you a vampire?"],[6227,6293,"Ella."],[6293,6393,"Let's just talk about this."],[6393,6464,"Okay?"],[6502,6573,"Get down."],[6835,6956,"Fine."],[7002,7115,"If that's your answer..."],[7365,7411,"Ella."],[7424,7482,"Ella!"],[7749,7778,"Ella!"]],"48":[[1209,1330,"Bring it in."],[1501,1543,"Next time"],[1543,1659,"your family is messing with you,"],[1659,1805,"just call me, alright?"],[1918,2035,"You can call me anytime."],[2139,2481,"In fact, every time you call me..."],[2494,2744,"I will be there in..."],[2831,2952,"three seconds or less."],[3712,3824,"One."],[3978,4099,"Two."],[4250,4354,"Three."],[5935,6056,"You kept your promise."],[6548,6652,"Vincent."],[6719,6806,"Wait!"],[6806,6886,"Don't touch me!"],[6886,7002,"Don't look at me."],[7148,7257,"Is this what you wanted?"],[7257,7378,"Ella Montgomery?"],[7499,7595,"Are you happy now?"]],"49":[[37,158,"This is who the real me is."],[483,600,"A monster."],[759,867,"A cold-hearted,"],[867,1017,"blood-sucking monster."],[2761,2882,"Ella, why?"],[3178,3299,"Because I love you."],[3486,3616,"No matter what you are."],[3712,3749,"Okay?"],[3749,3883,"It doesn't make a difference"],[3883,4062,"what you are, Vincent."],[4129,4220,"You could have told me"],[4220,4320,"about your true self back then."],[4320,4450,"I would have accepted you."],[4608,4792,"Loved you, even."],[4813,4925,"But..."],[4988,5155,"you chose to push me away."],[5409,5492,"Because you're so"],[5492,5588,"ashamed of yourself."],[5588,5772,"You turned our love into hate..."],[5826,6018,"for eight whole years."],[6039,6181,"Vincent."],[6577,6715,"Are you serious, Ella?"],[6961,7098,"You actually love me?"],[7169,7290,"Yeah."],[7340,7444,"I mean, I'm a vampire."],[7444,7565,"I could..."],[7570,7724,"I could kill you at any second."],[7866,7987,"Well."],[8012,8137,"I've always had a thing for jerks."],[8295,8420,"You got to be the biggest jerk"],[8420,8475,"of them all."],[8550,8671,"So what do you say?"],[8787,8908,"You love me?"],[8979,9059,"Ella, I love you,"],[9059,9196,"and I can't deny it anymore."],[9713,9847,"Oh, God."],[9968,10147,"I can't control myself."],[10222,10293,"Don't."],[10368,10447,"Love me with everything"],[10447,10527,"that you have."]],"50":[[3478,3561,"You want to bite me."],[3561,3632,"Don't you?"],[3632,3753,"Yeah, I do."],[3832,3953,"But I want to do other things"],[3953,4004,"to you..."],[4062,4183,"so much more."],[4633,4704,"I think we need to"],[4704,4859,"take some safety precautions."],[5030,5150,"Why do you have that?"],[5251,5367,"I got it when you moved in."],[5492,5655,"With a human sleeping next door,"],[5722,5834,"I get a little excited."]],"51":[[279,412,"Need a halftime break?"],[475,629,"God, are you really not tired?"],[788,892,"I stopped becoming tired"],[892,1013,"when I became a vampire."],[1297,1422,"When exactly did you?"],[1797,1918,"The day that we broke up."],[2085,2243,"My biological father tracked me down."],[2427,2786,"I allowed you to live long enough"],[2811,2948,"amongst humans."],[3015,3215,"It's time for you to join me."],[3269,3390,"Time for you"],[3415,3636,"to become a fully fledged vampire."],[3737,3970,"And swear your loyalty"],[4012,4454,"to me."],[4825,4992,"Is that why you broke up with me?"],[5242,5463,"Your father did this to you? Why?"],[5472,5572,"Why would he condemn you"],[5572,5668,"to such a cruel fate?"],[5739,5860,"Dimitri hates me."],[5951,6010,"He blames me"],[6010,6118,"for the death of the woman"],[6118,6177,"he loved most."]],"52":[[496,613,"This is my mother."],[654,838,"I promise I won't let Dimitri get to you."],[838,909,"But if you ever have"],[909,1051,"the misfortune of meeting him."],[1222,1338,"This should keep you protected."],[1488,1609,"I'm just confused."],[1801,1960,"Did you really kill your mother?"],[2081,2168,"I fed on her blood"],[2168,2289,"while I was in the womb."],[2310,2473,"Dimitri tried to save her, but..."],[2886,3007,"She didn't make it."],[3019,3161,"He tried to turn her into a vampire"],[3161,3286,"at the last second, but..."],[3424,3545,"it was too late."],[3645,3799,"And now he blames me for it."],[3912,4033,"And he hates me."],[4133,4300,"Honestly, I hate myself too."],[4441,4579,"Hey, that's not your fault."],[4783,5017,"As a mother myself, I can promise you."],[5121,5238,"She never blamed you."],[5242,5363,"Not once."],[5605,5705,"Is that why you stuck it out"],[5705,5797,"for our little vampire?"],[5943,6022,"I know it was difficult labor."],[6193,6314,"You found out?"],[6331,6443,"It's about time, right?"],[6756,6835,"But Ella."],[6835,6923,"I think it's time"],[6923,7044,"we give Jimmy a real family."],[7152,7269,"I know he wants it."],[7336,7453,"So do I."],[7640,7761,"I want that, too."],[8053,8179,"We just have to figure out"],[8241,8383,"when to tell Jimmy."],[8562,8683,"Maybe at his birthday party?"],[8917,9067,"I think that's a perfect idea."],[9718,9838,"A kid?"],[9939,10126,"Vincent has a kid?"],[10218,10335,"With a human?"],[10397,10514,"Yes. My lord."],[10739,10977,"What a perfect little family they must be."],[11207,11298,"Ella Montgomery."],[11298,11419,"Is it?"],[11553,11657,"This time."],[11657,11757,"Ella."],[11757,12062,"I will come see you for myself."]],"53":[[312,600,"Under investigation for financial fraud?"],[646,838,"Surprise surprise."],[880,930,"Oh."],[1051,1180,"Your dad again?"],[1201,1388,"Yeah, he..."],[1609,1743,"He says that he wants to come"],[1743,1830,"to Jimmy's birthday party."],[1843,1926,"Right? So he’s saying"],[1926,2006,"But obviously"],[2056,2177,"I know what he’s actually here for."],[2177,2289,"He wants Vincent"],[2289,2369,"to get him out of this mess"],[2369,2460,"that he’s got himself in."],[2460,2548,"Uncle Vincent!"],[2548,2698,"I want to help you with the cake."],[3219,3340,"Look at that."],[3432,3570,"Six..."],[3732,3849,"And then..."],[3933,4041,"eight!"],[4041,4162,"There we go."],[4671,4888,"You guys seem so happy together."],[4959,5155,"Okay, let me get out of your guys' hair,"],[5155,5288,"so you guys could celebrate."],[5288,5355,"Just the three of you."],[5380,5509,"What? No! Jimmy already said that"],[5509,5572,"you could have"],[5572,5676,"the biggest piece of cake."],[5789,5968,"Just tell him I'm on a sugar free diet."],[5985,6056,"He’s never gonna believe that."],[6056,6177,"I know right?"],[6318,6448,"Oh, but help me get his gift"],[6448,6577,"out of the car before I leave."],[6606,6740,"I really hope he likes it,"],[6740,6902,"because it was not cheap."],[6902,6986,"Not cheap?"],[7115,7265,"You’re gonna make me look bad."],[7399,7536,"Bye Fiona. Get home safe."],[7891,8062,"No more avoiding me, Ella."],[8128,8324,"If I take you, Vincent will"],[8324,8621,"have no choice but to help me."]],"54":[[0,216,"Whoa, what?"],[496,608,"Happy birthday, Jimmy."],[667,792,"Thanks, Uncle Vincent."],[821,905,"Wait."],[905,1030,"When I blow out the candles,"],[1030,1180,"can I wish for you to be my dad?"],[1263,1430,"Jimmy, you want me to be your dad?"],[1459,1580,"Of course."],[1597,1739,"You're so nice to me and mom."],[1755,1885,"You're my dream dad."],[1960,2135,"You're my dream son, kiddo."],[2173,2281,"Now go get your mom,"],[2281,2352,"alright?"],[2352,2473,"And when you get back,"],[2473,2590,"we're gonna make your wish"],[2590,2740,"and become one big family."],[3003,3186,"Better hurry, I'm gonna time you."],[4688,4804,"Ella."],[4846,5009,"Once this birthday party is over,"],[5042,5163,"I'm proposing to you."],[5305,5409,"Uncle Vincent."],[5409,5530,"Mommy's gone."],[5547,5655,"I can't find her."],[5655,5797,"Mommy's gone?"]],"55":[[563,738,"Boss, still no word on Ella."],[784,909,"But we found this by the door."],[1530,1651,"Dimitri."],[1735,1856,"That old bastard."],[1914,2010,"He wants me to come back."],[2010,2131,"Fine. I'll come back."],[2135,2281,"I'm going to fucking kill him this time."],[2431,2548,"Watch over Jimmy for me."],[4041,4162,"Oh my god, dad?"],[4667,4775,"I thought David kidnaped me."],[4775,4896,"Why is he dead?"],[4917,5038,"Why is he dead?"],[5042,5163,"You have me"],[5251,5372,"to thank for that."],[5472,5626,"Ella Montgomery."],[5747,5868,"I saved you."],[6731,6856,"You are Vincent's father."],[7057,7140,"You were the one"],[7140,7248,"who wants me dead."]],"56":[[291,362,"So..."],[387,437,"You thought"],[437,571,"you could outrun a vampire?"],[721,842,"How naive."],[1514,1689,"Let me have a look at you."],[1922,2018,"So..."],[2068,2156,"This..."],[2227,2373,"This is the beauty..."],[2423,2690,"who has captured my son's heart."],[2748,2869,"If it were not for you,"],[2952,3123,"Vincent would have obeyed"],[3161,3390,"He would have come back to me"],[3432,3661,"like he was supposed to."],[3903,4141,"You can't stand to see him happy."],[4166,4287,"Can you?"],[4341,4471,"That you made him feel like"],[4483,4600,"he killed his own mother."],[4600,4662,"What kind of"],[4662,4863,"spineless father are you?"],[4867,5092,"If he were not Marie's child,"],[5125,5280,"I would have killed him"],[5313,5434,"ages ago."],[5476,5580,"Why"],[5580,5659,"should the person"],[5659,5860,"who caused Marie's death"],[5860,6068,"get to find real love?"],[6101,6364,"Why should he get to find a woman"],[6377,6489,"who can give birth"],[6489,6765,"to a vampire child and survive?"],[6823,7190,"No. Vincent doesn't deserve happiness."],[7207,7557,"He should lose everything as I did."],[7632,7753,"He should suffer"],[7849,7995,"for all eternity."],[8204,8337,"No!"],[8337,8429,"My lord!"],[8429,8550,"Vincent's here!"],[9280,9355,"Give her back!"]],"57":[[62,204,"Vincent, help!"],[262,325,"Help!"],[354,571,"Vincent and Jimmy need me."],[571,700,"I can't die."],[2631,2748,"I just need to hold on"],[2748,2886,"until Vincent gets here."],[2965,3115,"What would Marie think of you?"],[3365,3445,"What would Marie think?"]],"58":[[287,350,"Look!"],[462,533,"Dimitri."],[567,779,"If Marie knew that you were trying"],[779,1005,"to destroy her son's life,"],[1155,1359,"she would hate you."],[1534,1655,"Shut up!"],[1793,1951,"You filthy liar!"],[1989,2310,"Who are you to speak for my wife?"],[2360,2481,"Who am I?"],[2552,2673,"I'm a mother!"],[2798,2919,"Just like Marie."],[2961,3086,"I have a little vampire boy,"],[3174,3399,"and I almost died giving birth to him."],[3399,3520,"Just like Marie."],[3524,3582,"And you know what?"],[3582,3699,"I would do it all over again."],[3699,3820,"You want to know why?"],[3899,4137,"Because I love Jimmy."],[4141,4262,"I love my son."],[4262,4425,"Just like I know for a fact"],[4446,4583,"Marie loves Vincent."],[4650,4767,"But you."],[4871,5109,"You turned him into a monster"],[5109,5184,"like yourself."],[5321,5426,"You made him"],[5426,5559,"leave the love of his life,"],[5559,5584,"made him"],[5584,5697,"suppress his feelings"],[5697,5789,"for years."],[5943,6097,"If Marie could see you now..."],[6398,6544,"she'd cry."],[6702,6848,"Enough to fill the ocean, she'd cry."],[6848,6956,"She'd be destroyed."],[7032,7148,"Lies!"],[7194,7394,"All lies!"],[7582,7703,"Ella..."],[7782,7899,"Montgomery."],[8045,8208,"I'm gonna rip..."],[8287,8408,"your heart out."],[8687,8804,"Dimitri!"],[8812,8946,"I'm coming for you."],[9467,9505,"Ella!"]],"59":[[429,542,"Ella, ella..."],[542,646,"No no no no no."],[658,721,"Ella."],[721,809,"Open your eyes."],[809,984,"Please, please open your eyes!"],[1080,1151,"I'm begging you!"],[1151,1222,"Please don't leave me."],[1247,1368,"Don't leave me. Please."],[1388,1555,"Please, Ella. Please."],[1697,1868,"I can see why you liked her, Vincent."],[1947,2114,"She has very tasty blood."],[2214,2335,"Welcome home."],[2360,2481,"Son."],[2823,2944,"You killed her."],[3249,3370,"You're dead, Dimitri."],[3432,3553,"You're fucking dead."],[4487,4558,"Yeah."],[4558,4612,"You know."]],"60":[[41,158,"You took her!"],[1522,1639,"Vincent."],[1993,2110,"Vincent."],[2248,2452,"Ella, ella. You're alive."],[2494,2615,"Thank god."],[2752,2857,"I won't ever leave you again."],[2857,2952,"I promise."],[3028,3219,"I won't leave you, but..."],[3520,3653,"I feel really weird."]],"61":[[25,204,"Did you turn me into a vampire?"],[379,513,"Did you do that to save me?"],[563,684,"What?"],[913,1034,"Dimitri, it was you."],[1101,1230,"She has better luck"],[1230,1351,"than your mother did."],[1572,1772,"But don't flatter yourself, son."],[1835,2047,"I didn't save her for you."],[2160,2277,"I did it for her."],[2435,2556,"And for her."],[2873,2990,"I couldn't live"],[3115,3311,"if I knew she hated me."],[3428,3574,"Using my mom for sympathy?"],[3632,3753,"Well, that's not gonna happen."],[3916,4054,"Hey."],[4116,4304,"I know he's done"],[4341,4462,"terrible things."],[4637,4758,"Look at me."],[4921,5055,"He's still Jimmy's grandpa,"],[5055,5234,"and I can't watch you to kill him."],[5234,5292,"I can't."],[5538,5659,"Let's go home."],[5739,5910,"Jimmy's birthday is almost over."],[5993,6143,"We promised to eat cake with him."],[6143,6297,"Remember?"],[7778,7824,"Vincent."]],"62":[[41,162,"Son."],[262,383,"Please."],[834,975,"You can try to stop me if you want,"],[975,1059,"but it'll be the last thing"],[1059,1151,"you ever fucking do."],[1272,1480,"Oh, what have I done."],[1559,1680,"And look at you."],[1735,1851,"Strong enough"],[1914,2106,"to resist your father's wishes."],[2310,2540,"Have I ever told you how much,"],[2540,2660,"you look like her?"],[2986,3107,"Please."],[3115,3165,"Son."],[3253,3628,"Just come and visit me"],[3678,3799,"once in a while."],[4062,4220,"I haven't dreamt of your mother"],[4387,4508,"in years."],[4625,4800,"I've missed her so much."],[4971,5067,"So so much."]],"63":[[646,696,"Wait,"],[788,921,"Jimmy can't see me like this."],[946,1055,"it's gonna freak him out."],[1101,1172,"You're right."],[1234,1305,"I'm so sorry."],[1305,1372,"Ella."],[1409,1509,"You're a vampire now,"],[1559,1643,"and it's all my fault."],[1647,1739,"I should have protected you"],[1739,1764,"better."],[1764,1856,"I can't believe—"],[1856,2043,"Hey, don't think like that, okay?"],[2239,2385,"Seriously, look on the bright side."],[2519,2761,"I won't get sick anymore."],[2836,2965,"And I won't age."],[3082,3390,"And I get to spend forever"],[3482,3603,"with you and Jimmy."],[3820,3970,"And now that I am"],[3970,4095,"part of the vampire gang."],[4191,4337,"I want to try teleporting."],[4337,4458,"I think it'd be so fun."],[5559,5680,"Oh, that was so fast."],[5689,5776,"We literally got here in, like,"],[5776,5897,"less than a minute."],[6310,6510,"What is this?"],[6694,6810,"It's a surprise."],[6856,6981,"Well, actually, it's a dress,"],[6981,7098,"to be more exact."],[7119,7190,"Go try it on,"],[7190,7286,"and then we can go see Jimmy."],[7457,7540,"I can't wait"],[7540,7707,"for Jimmy to find out what a kind"],[7770,7891,"and thoughtful,"],[8041,8174,"loving father he has."],[8329,8450,"Tonight's gonna be perfect."],[10047,10168,"I agree."],[10247,10352,"Tonight's gonna be amazing."]],"64":[[2936,3082,"You look like such a princess."],[3332,3453,"That makes you my prince."],[3657,3812,"I've waited so long for this."],[3999,4141,"Yeah, and I have to."],[5155,5251,"Shall we?"],[5438,5559,"We shall."],[6168,6289,"Is it because I..."],[6293,6443,"I asked for dad?"],[6481,6619,"Is that why mom left me?"],[6677,6798,"I promise"],[6802,6965,"I'll never ask for anything"],[6965,7048,"ever again."],[7123,7228,"All I want for my birthday"],[7228,7365,"is for mom to come back."],[7528,7657,"It's gonna be okay, kid."],[8287,8408,"Hey..."],[8571,8775,"There's no crying on your birthday."],[8779,8900,"Come here."],[9263,9413,"Mommy!"],[9451,9563,"Where did you go, mom?"],[9563,9738,"I thought you didn't want me anymore."],[9772,9868,"What?"],[9868,10055,"No, of course I want you."],[10060,10218,"I will always want you."],[10256,10385,"We just had to get ready for your party."],[10385,10506,"That's all."],[10527,10648,"All right."],[10652,10714,"Make sure you blow these candle out"],[10714,10819,"before midnight."]],"65":[[3682,3824,"Happy birthday, sweetheart."],[3837,3953,"Happy birthday, Jimmy."],[4074,4141,"All right, go ahead."],[4141,4250,"Make a wish."],[4250,4320,"But..."],[4354,4579,"I already wished for you to come back,"],[4579,4654,"mom."],[4683,4821,"Can I wish for something else?"],[4867,4975,"Of course you can, Jimmy."],[4975,5096,"A great kid like you."],[5113,5226,"You can make as many wishes"],[5226,5276,"as you want."],[5359,5455,"Wish away."],[5935,6056,"Okay, I got it."],[6072,6202,"Wow. Okay."],[6202,6318,"What is your wish for?"],[6352,6477,"I wish for Uncle Vincent"],[6477,6577,"to be my dad."],[7044,7111,"Jimmy, I have something"],[7111,7186,"I need to tell you."],[7261,7378,"What is it?"],[7382,7503,"I already am your dad."],[7807,7928,"Always have been."],[8124,8187,"Eight years ago,"],[8187,8341,"your mother and I had you, but..."],[8504,8646,"Fate tore us apart."],[8879,9063,"But now it's brought us back together."],[9225,9280,"Really?"],[9280,9430,"So I can call you dad now?"],[9455,9576,"Wait, dad!"],[9601,9718,"You're my dad?"],[9943,10060,"I love you, Jimmy."],[10176,10231,"And you know what?"],[10231,10368,"To make up for the last eight years,"],[10460,10510,"I'm gonna let you"],[10510,10606,"witness something special."]],"66":[[137,283,"Vincent, when did you get that?"],[462,579,"Eight years ago."],[696,804,"If Dimitri hadn't shown up,"],[804,925,"I never would have left you."],[1005,1126,"And I was gonna propose to you"],[1126,1159,"that day"],[1159,1276,"with the same ring."],[1564,1739,"So I wasn't imagining things."],[1947,2081,"You really were gonna propose"],[2081,2139,"that day?"],[2248,2364,"I was."],[2569,2644,"Ella, this ring,"],[2644,2769,"has always belonged to you."],[3048,3211,"I want to spend a thousand lifetimes"],[3211,3278,"with you and Jimmy."],[3278,3395,"The three of us."],[4225,4346,"Will you marry me?"],[4408,4491,"Say yes."],[4491,4617,"Mom, please."],[4971,5276,"Yes...Yes!"],[6589,6831,"You're stuck with me now my love."],[7774,7949,"I know it's not official yet, but..."],[8087,8208,"Can I call you my wife?"],[8304,8425,"For eternity?"],[8512,8629,"Absolutely."],[8692,8808,"My forever husband."],[9530,9713,"This is the best birthday ever."],[9718,9759,"Good!"]]}